2000;74:115-9.
9. Suputtamongkol Y, Hall AJ, Dance DA, et al. The epidemiology of
melioidosis in Ubon Ratchatani, northeast Thailand. Int J Epidemiol.
1994;23:1082-90.
10. Currie BJ, Fisher DA, Howard DM, et al. Endemic melioidosis in
tropical northern Australia: a 10-year prospective study and review
of the literature. Clin Infect Dis. 2000;31:981-6.
