[The case of melioidosis expands the documented range of _B.
pseudomallei_ infection. Since melioidosis is a category B biowarfare
agent, documenting its natural range is important. The flooding
caused by the recent tsunami involved areas of endemicity for
melioidosis, and it should be watched for in these areas. - Mod.LL]
